                        Shine On You Crazy Diamond (Part 2)
                               Wish You Were Here
                                  Pink Floyd

Tabbed by Ste Waugh
stephen_waugh@hotmail.co.uk

NOTE:
Tablatures are used as a shorthand, so you cannot expect to have everything
 you need in this tab, e.g Time elements.
Make sure you have the song playing whilst you are using this, so you can
 suit to the timing, and adjust it how you feel.


Setup:

 - Standard tuning
 - Tough guitarist fingers (there is a fair amount of bends)
 - Dave Gilmour plays this on his Fender Stratocaster
   using the neck pickup, heavily compressed sound and reverb.

Play:

 - In Free time, there isnt any rythm guitar or drum in this piece.


