     ====================================================================
                                   Legend
     ====================================================================


| >               - Bend the note
| <               - Release bend
| ~~~~~~~~~~~     - Vibrato
| hold bend ----|­­­­­­­­­­ - Hold bend
| (n)             - Desired note to bend to
| /               - Slide up
| \               - Slide down
| pr              - Pre-bend
| p               - Pull off
| h               - Hammer-on

